code: public GenericFile<T> renameFile(Exchange exchange, GenericFile<T> file) {     ObjectHelper.notNull(expression, "expression").     String newName = expression.evaluate(exchange, String.class).     // make a copy as result and change its file name     GenericFile<T> result = file.copyFrom(file).     result.changeFileName(newName).     return result. }
